<p><strong>7</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Einzug</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Über diese Icons den <strong>Einzug</strong> eines Abschnitts <strong>erhöhen</strong> oder <strong>verringern</strong>.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
